OL,3,CO'Neill accuses DUP of 'spoofing' over
OL,4,Cclaims Sinn Fein fails to support PSNI
OL,6,FA rift has emerged between the First
OL,7,Fand deputy First Ministers over
OL,8,Fpolicing, following the dissident bomb
OL,9,Fattack in Dunmurry.
OL,11,FMichelle O'Neill accused the DUP of
OL,12,F"spoofing" over claims that her party
OL,13,Fhas failed to support the PSNI.
OL,15,FEmma Little Pengelly said there is a
OL,16,Fneed for "grown up politics" and that
OL,17,Fis not a term that she would use.
OL,26,@lD@Nrr
