OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777493189
OL,3,CO'Neill accuses DUP of 'spoofing' over
OL,4,Cclaims Sinn Fein fails to support PSNI
OL,6,FThe PSNI were targeted when a delivery
OL,7,Fdriver who had been hijacked in
OL,8,FTwinbrook, was forced to leave a bomb
OL,9,Foutside Dunmurry police station on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,FThe New IRA attack was jointly
OL,13,Fcondemned by political leaders and the
OL,14,Fchief constable on Monday, in what was
OL,15,Fa deliberate show of solidarity.
OL,17,FHowever, the DUP Leader accused Sinn
OL,18,FFein of failing to support the police.
OL,26,@lD@NrrzD@Brr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777493189
OL,3,CO'Neill accuses DUP of 'spoofing' over
OL,4,Cclaims Sinn Fein fails to support PSNI
OL,6,FSpeaking on Monday, Gavin Robinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "When the Chief Constable
OL,8,Fvisited a school in Twinbrook last
OL,9,Fweek and was slammed online by
OL,10,Fdissident republicans and their
OL,11,Fsupporters, I heard nothing from Sinn
OL,12,FFein or their leadership."
OL,14,FThe First and deputy First Ministers
OL,15,Fstood side by side at the signing of
OL,16,Fthe Causeway Coast and Glens growth
OL,17,Fdeal in Limavady on Wednesday.
OL,26,@lD@NrrtD@Brr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
