OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777493189
OL,3,CO'Neill accuses DUP of 'spoofing' over
OL,4,Cclaims Sinn Fein fails to support PSNI
OL,6,FMichelle O'Neill said: "There's no
OL,7,Fquestion of our support for policing.
OL,8,FI think this is an argument that's
OL,9,Fbeen advanced by Gavin Robinson`he's
OL,10,Fbeen found out to be spoofing.
OL,12,F"The DUP are actually spoofing and
OL,13,Fdistracting from actually the real
OL,14,Fmessage that people at home want to
OL,15,Fhear, which is that we are united in
OL,16,Fsaying 'no' to those people that want
OL,17,Fto drag us back."
OL,26,@lD@Nrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
