FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777493189
OL,3,CO'Neill accuses DUP of 'spoofing' over
OL,4,Cclaims Sinn Fein fails to support PSNI
OL,6,FEmma Little-Pengelly said: "Well, it
OL,7,Fwouldn't be the type of language I
OL,8,Fwould use. I think what people want
OL,9,Fout there is grown-up politics.
OL,11,F"I think people want their politicians
OL,12,Fto take things seriously. And, of
OL,13,Fcourse, this is a very serious issue."
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Sinn Fein's Liz Kimmins
OL,16,Fstood with a senior PSNI officer to
OL,17,Fappeal for road safety.
OL,26,@lD@NrrwD@Rrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
