FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777493189
OL,3,CO'Neill accuses DUP of 'spoofing' over
OL,4,Cclaims Sinn Fein fails to support PSNI
OL,6,FThe Infrastructure Minister dismissed
OL,7,Fany suggestion there was a difficulty
OL,8,Fwith the police and said actions speak
OL,9,Flouder than words.
OL,11,FMs Kimmons said: "We're here to
OL,12,Fdeliver a very important public safety
OL,13,Fmessage because this is about
OL,14,Fprotecting people's lives."
OL,16,FAnalysis:
OL,18,FThere appears to be a change of tone
OL,19,Ffrom Michelle O'Neill.
OL,26,@lD@Nrr
