OL,3,CO'Neill accuses DUP of 'spoofing' over
OL,4,Cclaims Sinn Fein fails to support PSNI
OL,6,FPerhaps, she is mindful of her claim
OL,7,Fto be a First Minister for all.
OL,9,FShe has, for the most part, stayed out
OL,10,Fof public attacks on her partners in
OL,11,Fgovernment, the DUP.
OL,13,FHowever, that has changed in recent
OL,14,Fdays.
OL,16,FIt was most notable at Sinn Fein's Ard
OL,17,FFheis at the weekend and now in the
OL,18,Fface of DUP criticism about Sinn
OL,19,FFein's attitude towards the police.
OL,26,@lD@NrrxD@^rr
