OL,3,CO'Neill accuses DUP of 'spoofing' over
OL,4,Cclaims Sinn Fein fails to support PSNI
OL,6,FIf this is a new approach, it could
OL,7,Fmean relations between the two main
OL,8,Fparties will sour even more.
